<Body>    <Title>手机充电器爆炸引发大火 致2死2伤</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2009-08-04</ReportTime>
	<Content>	

		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e1"><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">昨日凌晨</Time>，发生在<Location lid="l1">海珠区南村路一民居</Location>的一场<Denoter did="d1" type="emergency">大火</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e2">导致家中<Participant sid="s2">两位老人</Participant><Denoter did="d2" type="stateChange">死亡</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e3"><Participant sid="s3">女主人跟小女儿</Participant><Denoter did="d3" type="stateChange">受伤</Denoter></Event>，<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e4">根据<Participant sid="s4">警方</Participant>初步<Denoter did="d4" type="operation">调查</Denoter>结果</Event>，是<Event eid="e5"><Object sid="s5">电路</Object><Denoter did="d5" type="stateChange">短路</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e6">导致<Object sid="s6">手机充电器</Object><Denoter did="d6" type="emergency">爆炸</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e7">引发<Denoter did="d7" type="emergency">火灾</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　  <Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e8"><Time tid="t8" type="relTime">昨日凌晨2时30分</Time>，<Participant sid="s8">记者</Participant><Denoter did="d8" type="movement">赶到</Denoter><Location lid="l8" type="destination">南村路事故现场</Location>时</Event>，<Event eid="e9"><Object oid="o9">大火</Object>已基本被<Participant sid="s9">消防员</Participant><Denoter did="d9" type="stateChange">扑灭</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e10">由于<Object oid="o10">险情</Object>仍未最后<Denoter did="d10" type="operation">排除</Denoter>，</Event><Event polarity="negative" eid="e11">大批受影响的<Participant sid="s11,s12,s13">居民</Participant>不能<Denoter did="d11" type="movement">回家</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e12"><Denoter did="d12" type="action">站</Denoter>在<Location lid="l12">路边</Location></Event><Event eid="e13"><Denoter did="d13" type="perception">观望</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence>起火的确切地址为南村路113号501房，起火时间为凌晨1时左右。</Sentence><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e14">一名住在对面楼房5楼的<Participant sid="s14">住户</Participant><Denoter did="d14" type="statement">说</Denoter></Event>：“<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e15"><Participant sid="s15">我</Participant><Denoter type="perception" did="d15">看到</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e16"><Location lid="l16">对面楼501房</Location><Denoter did="d16" type="action">冒</Denoter>出大量的<Object oid="o16">黑烟</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e17"><Participant sid="s17,s18,s19">一对母女</Participant><Denoter did="d17" type="action">站</Denoter>在<Location lid="l17">阳台</Location></Event><Event eid="e18"><Denoter did="d18" type="action">抓着</Denoter><Object oid="o18">防盗网</Object></Event><Event eid="e19">大<Denoter did="d19" type="action">呼</Denoter>救命</Event>。”</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e20">大院当晚值班看门的<Participant sid="s20">何先生</Participant><Denoter did="d20" type="statement">称</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e21" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s21,s23,s24">他</Participant>最先<Denoter did="d21" type="perception">发现</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e22"><Location lid="l22">501房</Location><Denoter did="d22" type="action">冒烟</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e23">于是大声<Denoter did="d23" type="action">呼叫</Denoter>住户起床逃生</Event><Event eid="e24">并<Denoter did="d24" type="operation">报警</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e25"><Participant sid="s25">何先生</Participant><Denoter did="d25" type="statement">说</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e26">很快<Participant sid="s26,s27">消防队员</Participant><Denoter did="d26" type="action">破门而入</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e27">将房间中的<Participant oid="o27">两母女</Participant><Denoter did="d27" type="operation">救出</Denoter>火海</Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>“那家人我认识，女人叫阿琼，<Event eid="e28"><Denoter did="d28" type="operation">救</Denoter>下来</Event>时还能说话，<Event eid="e29"><Participant sid="s29">她</Participant><Denoter did="d29" type="statement">说</Denoter></Event>她的父母还在屋内。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e30">接着<Participant sid="s30" oid="o31">她们</Participant>被<Denoter did="d30" type="movement">送去</Denoter><Location lid="l30">医院</Location></Event><Event eid="e31"><Denoter did="d31" type="operation">抢救</Denoter></Event>。”</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e32"><Time tid="t32" type="relTime">3时30分</Time>，<Object oid="o32">险情</Object>基本<Denoter did="d32" type="operation">排除</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e33"><Participant sid="s33,s34">民警与消防队员</Participant>上门<Denoter did="d33" type="operation">搜索</Denoter></Event>，<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e34"><Denoter did="d34" type="perception">证实</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e35"><Participant sid="s35">两位老人</Participant>已在大火中<Denoter did="d35" type="stateChange">丧生</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
	
